snippet.title: L U C A H ~ Kickstarter Trailer ~
snippet.description:
Support L U C A H now on Kickstarter!
https://bit.ly/lucahgame

L U C A H is a style-action role-playing game about finding oneself in a nightmarish world, coming to PC, Mac, and Linux in 2018.

Try the demo now at https://melessthanthree.itch.io/lucah.

Follow us for more information at:
https://www.facebook.com/lucahgame
https://www.twitter.com/melessthanthree
https://lucahgame.tumblr.com
